script.name: al.SWLU.Tick
script.description: LitQB's Phanon Corporation: Main timer routine

line.comment: * This script is mainly only used to initialize SWLU right now. The grand campaigns will come later ;)
* This script starts after 15 seconds of playing time to give the universe a second to settle/load
* al engine: set plugin $plugin.ID timer interval to 180 s
* al engine: set plugin $plugin.ID timer interval to 15 s
* All Plugin Variables are explained in the MAIN routine.
* Excludes the welcome message for ship gallery and survival mode
* War declarations accross the vanilla factions to resemble conflicts in star wars
* Removes any and all Xenon fighters form the player's starting sector
* Totally not repurposed code from Litcube's Phanon Corporation lol
* Buffs any marines the player might have on their ship (not external ships)
